title: Traveling to Islamabad
description: Me and my colleagues from University of Karachi were finally invited to COMSTECH Conference. We went there by train and had a wonderful time watching the enchanting scenery.

title: Arrived @ COMSTECH
description: After a long journey we finally arrived at COMSTECH. We relieved ourselves of our exhaustion thanks to the hospitality and awaited the morning when we would attend the conference.

title: Praying @ Shah Faisal Masjid
description: We had planned a few side trips in our 3-day stay at COMSTECH. This trip was dedicated to offering our Jumma prayer in Shah Faisal Masjid. It was an enlightening experience to stand behind the Imam of the Masjid

title: Visiting Daman-e-Koh
description: We also visited Daman-e-Koh but for a very limited span of time. Our departure was due and we were planning on one last sight seeing expedition.
